# Common Interview Mistakes

❌

```java
int age = sc.nextInt();

String name = sc.nextLine();
```

The name becomes an empty string.

---

✅

```java
int age = sc.nextInt();

sc.nextLine();

String name = sc.nextLine();
```

Correct.

---

❌

```java
char ch = sc.nextChar();
```

Compilation Error.

---

✅

```java
char ch = sc.next().charAt(0);
```

Correct.

---

