# Revision Box

✅ next() → Reads one word.

✅ nextLine() → Reads the entire line.

✅ nextInt() leaves `\n` in the input buffer.

✅ nextLine() reads the leftover newline if not consumed.

✅ Fix → Add an extra `sc.nextLine()` before reading the full line.

✅ Scanner has no `nextChar()` method.

✅ Read a character using:

```java
sc.next().charAt(0);
```

